00:42:34.510 --> 00:42:36.590
But it really depends
on the overall beer

00:42:36.590 --> 00:42:38.400
that you're cooking with.

00:42:38.400 --> 00:42:40.790
I try to be as specific
as possible in the book,

00:42:40.790 --> 00:42:43.130
